<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Recarregar Carteira do Driver</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1d4ed8);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 520px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
      padding: 32px;
    }
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .hero p {
      color: #4b5563;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .notice {
      background: #eff6ff;
      border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
      color: #1e3a8a;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 18px; }
    label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #1f2937;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    input, select {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
      background: #fff;
    }
    input:focus, select:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #2563eb;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
    }
    .phone-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 88px 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .prefix {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #f9fafb;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .providers {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .provider {
      border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      transition: .2s ease;
      background: #f9fafb;
    }
    .provider.active {
      border-color: #2563eb;
      background: #eff6ff;
    }
    .provider img {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      object-fit: contain;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 4px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .provider strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .provider small {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .button {
      width: 100%;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a, #15803d);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .button:disabled {
      opacity: .7;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }
    .status {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
      display: none;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .status.info { display: block; background: #eff6ff; color: #1d4ed8; }
    .status.success { display: block; background: #ecfdf5; color: #166534; }
    .status.error { display: block; background: #fef2f2; color: #b91c1c; }
    .meta {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .card { padding: 22px; }
      .providers { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Checkout do Driver</h1>
      <p>Recarregue a carteira usando o numero de telefone registado do motorista.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="notice">
      O telefone identifica o driver automaticamente no ONDE.<br>
      `84/85` usam M-Pesa e `86/87` usam e-Mola.
    </div>

    <form id="driverCheckoutForm">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="phone">Telefone do driver</label>
        <div class="phone-row">
          <div class="prefix">+258</div>
          <input id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="9" placeholder="84xxxxxxx" required>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="amount">Valor</label>
        <input id="amount" name="amount" type="number" min="1" step="0.01" value="<%= defaultAmount %>" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="provider">Metodo</label>
        <select id="provider" name="provider">
          <option value="mpesa">M-Pesa</option>
          <option value="emola">e-Mola</option>
        </select>
        <div class="providers" id="providerCards">
          <div class="provider active" data-provider="mpesa" id="provider-mpesa">
            <img src="/images/mpesa.png" alt="M-Pesa">
            <div><strong>M-Pesa</strong><small>Recomendado para 84 e 85</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="provider" data-provider="emola" id="provider-emola">
            <img src="/images/emola.webp" alt="e-Mola">
            <div><strong>e-Mola</strong><small>Recomendado para 86 e 87</small></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="button" id="submitButton" type="submit">Recarregar carteira</button>
    </form>

    <div class="status" id="statusBox"></div>

    <div class="meta">
      Moeda: <%= defaultCurrency %> · O sistema cria invoice, cobra e faz commit automatico no ONDE.
    </div>
  </div>

  <script id="driver-checkout-data" type="application/json">
    {
      "currency": "<%= defaultCurrency %>"
    }
  </script>
  <script src="/js/driver-checkout.js?v=<%= Date.now() %>"></script>
</body>
</html>
